{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":857,"text":"According to the theories\nof human social development,"},{"time":3719,"text":"we're now living\nthrough the fourth great epoch"},{"time":5960,"text":"of technological advancement,"},{"time":8080,"text":"the Information Age."},{"time":10240,"text":"Connectivity through digital technology\nis a modern miracle."},{"time":13840,"text":"We can say it has broken down barriers\nof time and space which separate people,"},{"time":19000,"text":"and it's created a condition for an age"},{"time":20920,"text":"where information, ideas\ncan be shared freely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25240,"text":"But are these great accomplishments\nin digital technology"},{"time":28200,"text":"really the endgame\nin terms of what can be achieved?"},{"time":31640,"text":"I don't think so,"},{"time":33080,"text":"and today I'd like to share with you"},{"time":34880,"text":"how I believe digital technology\ncan take us to even greater heights."},{"time":39880,"text":"I'm a surgeon by profession,"},{"time":41840,"text":"and as I stand here today\ntalking to all of you,"},{"time":44240,"text":"five billion people around the world\nlack access to safe surgical care."},{"time":48640,"text":"Five billion people."},{"time":51080,"text":"That's 70 percent\nof the world's population,"},{"time":53720,"text":"who according to the WHO's\nLancet Commission"},{"time":56200,"text":"can't even access\nsimple surgical procedures"},{"time":59000,"text":"as and when they need them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61760,"text":"Let's zoom in on Sierra Leone,"},{"time":63840,"text":"a country of six million people,"},{"time":66360,"text":"where a recent study showed\nthat there are only 10 qualified surgeons."},{"time":70520,"text":"That's one surgeon\nfor every 600,000 people."},{"time":74280,"text":"The numbers are staggering,"},{"time":76680,"text":"and we don't even need to look that far."},{"time":79160,"text":"If we look around us here in the US,"},{"time":81320,"text":"a recent study reported that we need\nan extra 100,000 surgeons by 2030"},{"time":86080,"text":"to just keep up with the demand\nfor routine surgical procedures."},{"time":90120,"text":"At the rate that we're going,\nwe won't be meeting those numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95520,"text":"As a surgeon, this is\na global issue that bothers me."},{"time":98160,"text":"It bothers me a lot,"},{"time":99720,"text":"because I've seen firsthand"},{"time":101560,"text":"how lack of access\nto safe and affordable healthcare"},{"time":104440,"text":"can blight the lives of ordinary people."},{"time":106960,"text":"If you're a patient\nthat needs an operation"},{"time":109080,"text":"and there isn't a surgeon available,"},{"time":110840,"text":"you're left with some\nreally difficult choices:"},{"time":113840,"text":"to wait, to travel,"},{"time":117200,"text":"or not to have an operation at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120880,"text":"So what's the answer?"},{"time":123000,"text":"Well, part of you are carrying\nsome of that solution with you today:"},{"time":127120,"text":"a smartphone, a tablet, a computer."},{"time":131080,"text":"Because for me,"},{"time":132480,"text":"digital communications technology\nhas the power to do so much more"},{"time":136560,"text":"than just to allow us to shop online,"},{"time":138840,"text":"to connect through social media platforms\nand to stay up to date."},{"time":142880,"text":"It has the power to help us solve\nsome of the key issues that we face,"},{"time":147120,"text":"like lack of access\nto vital surgical services."},{"time":150440,"text":"And today I'd like to share with you"},{"time":152200,"text":"an example of how I think\nwe can make that possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155360,"text":"The history of surgery\nis filled with breakthroughs"},{"time":157800,"text":"in how science and technology\nwas able to help the surgeons of the day"},{"time":161160,"text":"face their greatest challenges."},{"time":162680,"text":"If we go back several hundred years,"},{"time":164680,"text":"an understanding of microbiology"},{"time":166600,"text":"led to the development\nof antiseptic techniques,"},{"time":168960,"text":"which played a big role in making sure"},{"time":170840,"text":"patients were able\nto stay alive postsurgery."},{"time":173200,"text":"Fast-forward a few hundred years"},{"time":174800,"text":"and we developed\nkeyhole or arthroscopic surgery,"},{"time":177160,"text":"which combines video technology\nand precision instruments"},{"time":180080,"text":"to make surgery less invasive."},{"time":183760,"text":"And more recently, a lot of you\nwill be aware of robotic surgery,"},{"time":187120,"text":"and what robotics brings to surgery\nis much like modern automated machinery,"},{"time":191800,"text":"ultraprecision,"},{"time":193680,"text":"the ability to carry out procedures\nat the tiniest scales"},{"time":197120,"text":"with a degree of accuracy\nthat even surpasses the human hand."},{"time":202000,"text":"But robotic surgery also introduced\nsomething else to surgery:"},{"time":206480,"text":"the idea that a surgeon"},{"time":207960,"text":"doesn't actually have to be standing\nat the patient's bedside to deliver care,"},{"time":212320,"text":"that he could be looking at a screen"},{"time":214240,"text":"and instructing a robot\nthrough a computer."},{"time":217800,"text":"We call this remote surgery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222800,"text":"It is incumbent on us"},{"time":224520,"text":"to find solutions that solve these answers\nin a cost-effective and scalable way,"},{"time":229000,"text":"so that everyone, no matter\nwhere they are in the world,"},{"time":231680,"text":"can have these problems addressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234440,"text":"So what if I told you"},{"time":236120,"text":"that you didn't really need\na million-dollar robot"},{"time":238520,"text":"to provide remote surgery?"},{"time":240720,"text":"That all you needed\nwas a phone, a tablet, or a computer,"},{"time":245680,"text":"an internet connection,"},{"time":247800,"text":"a confident colleague on the ground"},{"time":249640,"text":"and one magic ingredient:"},{"time":252120,"text":"an augmented reality\ncollaboration software."},{"time":256079,"text":"Using this augmented reality\ncollaboration software,"},{"time":258839,"text":"an expert surgeon\ncan now virtually transport himself"},{"time":261920,"text":"into any clinical setting"},{"time":263720,"text":"simply by using his phone\nor tablet or computer,"},{"time":266800,"text":"and he can visually and practically\ninteract in an operation"},{"time":269680,"text":"from start to finish,"},{"time":271040,"text":"guiding and mentoring a local doctor\nthrough the procedure step by step."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275800,"text":"Well, enough of me telling you about it."},{"time":278040,"text":"I'd now like to show you."},{"time":282840,"text":"We're now going to go live\nto Dr. Marc Tompkins,"},{"time":285800,"text":"an orthopedic surgeon\nat the University of Minnesota."},{"time":289800,"text":"He's going to perform\nan arthroscopic surgery for us,"},{"time":292320,"text":"a keyhole surgery of the knee,"},{"time":294520,"text":"and I'd like to disclose"},{"time":296080,"text":"that this patient has consented\nto having their operation streamed."},{"time":302040,"text":"I'd also like to point out\nthat in the interest of time,"},{"time":304720,"text":"we're just going to go\nthrough the first steps,"},{"time":306960,"text":"marking up the patient"},{"time":308240,"text":"and just identifying\na few key anatomical landmarks."},{"time":312960,"text":"Hello, Dr. Tompkins, can you hear me?"},{"time":316200,"text":"Dr. Mark Tompkins: Good morning, Nadine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318200,"text":"Nadine Hachach-Haram:\nEveryone from TED says hello."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320640,"text":"Audience: Hi."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324200,"text":"NHH: Alright, Dr. Tompkins,\nlet's get started."},{"time":326520,"text":"So let's start with our incisions\nand where we're going to make these,"},{"time":329840,"text":"on either side of the patellar tendon."},{"time":331800,"text":"So if you can make\nyour incisions there and there,"},{"time":335520,"text":"that should hopefully\nget us into the knee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"MT: All right, I'm going in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341840,"text":"NHH: Great."},{"time":345480,"text":"So we're just getting\ninside the joint now."},{"time":350520,"text":"So why don't we go around\nand have a quick look at the meniscus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355680,"text":"MT: Perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359960,"text":"NHH: Great, so we can see there's\na small tear there on the meniscus,"},{"time":363520,"text":"but otherwise it looks alright."},{"time":366800,"text":"And if you turn\nand head to this direction,"},{"time":369240,"text":"follow my finger,"},{"time":370480,"text":"let's have a quick look\nat the ACL and the PCL."},{"time":374720,"text":"That's your ACL there,\nthat looks quite healthy,"},{"time":377960,"text":"no problems there."},{"time":379240,"text":"So we've just identified\nthat small meniscus tear there,"},{"time":382280,"text":"but otherwise the fluid\naround the joint looks OK as well."},{"time":386920,"text":"All right, thank you very much,\nDr. Tompkins. Thank you for your time."},{"time":390280,"text":"I'll let you continue."},{"time":391920,"text":"Have a good day. Bye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":402840,"text":"So I hope through\nthis simple demonstration"},{"time":404920,"text":"I was able to illustrate to you\njust how powerful this technology can be."},{"time":408840,"text":"And I'd like to point out\nthat I wasn't using any special equipment,"},{"time":412080,"text":"just my laptop and a really simple webcam."},{"time":414560,"text":"We're so used to using digital technology"},{"time":416560,"text":"to communicate through voice\nand text and video,"},{"time":419760,"text":"but augmented reality\ncan do something so much deeper."},{"time":423080,"text":"It allows two people to virtually interact"},{"time":425400,"text":"in a way that mimics\nhow they would collaborate in person."},{"time":429200,"text":"Being able to show someone\nwhat you want to do,"},{"time":431440,"text":"to illustrate and demonstrate and gesture,"},{"time":433600,"text":"is so much more powerful\nthan just telling them."},{"time":436840,"text":"And it can make\nfor such a great learning tool,"},{"time":439080,"text":"because we learn better\nthrough direct experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442040,"text":"So how is this making\na difference around the world?"},{"time":444520,"text":"Well, back in my teaching hospital,"},{"time":446600,"text":"we've been using this to support\nlocal district general hospitals"},{"time":449720,"text":"and providing skin cancer surgery\nand trauma treatment."},{"time":452800,"text":"Now, patients can access\ncare at a local level."},{"time":456200,"text":"This reduces their travel time,\nimproves their access,"},{"time":459560,"text":"and saves money."},{"time":461680,"text":"We've even started seeing its use\nin wound care management with nurses"},{"time":465000,"text":"and in outpatient management."},{"time":466760,"text":"Most recently, and quite exciting,"},{"time":468520,"text":"it was used in supporting a surgeon\nthrough a cancer removal of a kidney."},{"time":474320,"text":"And I'd like to just share with you\na very quick video here."},{"time":477760,"text":"I apologize for some\nof the gruesome views."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482080,"text":"(Video) Doctor 1: OK. Show me again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485760,"text":"Doctor 2: If you see here,"},{"time":487880,"text":"that's the upper part,\nthe most outer part of your tumor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491960,"text":"Doctor 1: Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493240,"text":"Doctor 2: So it's\nthree centimeters deep,"},{"time":496120,"text":"so this should be three centimeters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498840,"text":"Doctor 1: Yes, yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500200,"text":"Doctor 2: OK,\nso you need to get a 3.5 margin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505536,"text":"Doctor 1: I'm going to show you anyway"},{"time":507560,"text":"and tell me what you think about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510880,"text":"NHH: We're also seeing the use\nof this technology at a global scale,"},{"time":514280,"text":"and one of the most\nheartwarming stories I can recall"},{"time":516840,"text":"is from the town of Trujillo\nin the north of Lima in Peru,"},{"time":520840,"text":"where this technology\nwas used to support the provision"},{"time":523720,"text":"of cleft lip and palate\nsurgery to children,"},{"time":526360,"text":"children from poor backgrounds who\ndidn't have access to health insurance."},{"time":530360,"text":"And in this town, there was\na hospital with one surgeon"},{"time":533000,"text":"working hard to provide this care,"},{"time":534960,"text":"Dr. Soraya."},{"time":536960,"text":"Now, Dr. Soraya was struggling\nunder the sheer demand"},{"time":539480,"text":"of her local population,"},{"time":540920,"text":"as well as the fact that she wasn't\nspecifically trained in this procedure."},{"time":544520,"text":"And so, with the help of a charity,"},{"time":546240,"text":"we were able to connect her\nwith a cleft surgeon in California,"},{"time":549720,"text":"and using this technology, he was able\nto guide her and her colleagues"},{"time":553040,"text":"through the procedure step by step,"},{"time":554760,"text":"guiding them, training them\nand teaching them."},{"time":556960,"text":"Within a few months,"},{"time":558240,"text":"they were able to perform\n30 percent more operations"},{"time":560720,"text":"with less and less complications."},{"time":562840,"text":"And now Dr. Soraya and her team\ncan perform these operations"},{"time":566280,"text":"independently, competently\nand confidently."},{"time":570000,"text":"And I remember one quote\nfrom a mother who said,"},{"time":572800,"text":"\"This technology\ngave my daughter her smile.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":576640,"text":"For me, this is the real power\nof this technology."},{"time":579800,"text":"The beauty is that it breaks boundaries."},{"time":582200,"text":"It transcends all\ntechnological difficulties."},{"time":586520,"text":"It connects people.\nIt democratizes access."},{"time":590160,"text":"Wi-Fi and mobile technology\nare growing rapidly,"},{"time":592440,"text":"and they should play a role\nin boosting surgical provision."},{"time":595480,"text":"We've even seen it used in conflict zones\nwhere there's considerable risk"},{"time":598960,"text":"in getting specialist surgeons\nto certain locations."},{"time":601520,"text":"In a world where\nthere are more mobile devices"},{"time":604440,"text":"than there are human beings,"},{"time":606320,"text":"it truly has a global reach."},{"time":608920,"text":"Of course, we've still got a long way"},{"time":610760,"text":"before we can solve the problem\nof getting surgery to five billion people,"},{"time":614280,"text":"and unfortunately,"},{"time":615560,"text":"some people still\ndon't have access to internet."},{"time":618520,"text":"But things are rapidly moving\nin the right direction."},{"time":622360,"text":"The potential for change is there."},{"time":624840,"text":"My team and I are growing\nour global footprint,"},{"time":627800,"text":"and we're starting to see\nthe potential of this technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632440,"text":"Through digital technology,"},{"time":634360,"text":"through simple, everyday devices\nthat we take for granted,"},{"time":637680,"text":"through devices of the future,"},{"time":639720,"text":"we can really do miraculous things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642360,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643600,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}